
 Makefile Option: Silent Compile
================================
(like 'CC ..')


1. in <configure>
 add the following switch "--enable-silent-rules"

2. in <configure.ac>
 add "AM_SILENT_RULES" macros 

3. when doing 'make'
 make V=0|1  (VERBOSE)



 Expend command before executing
================================
  make SHELL='sh -x'
